               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Daily Office Prayers and Litanies (fols. 1ra-4va). Incomplete
 II)
                     Anaphoras
 II-1) Anaphora of the Apostles (incipit fol. 4va, explicit fol.
                     18vb)
 II-2) Anaphora of St Dioscorus of Alexandria (incipit fol. 19ra,
                     explicit fol. 31ra)
 II-3) Anaphora of St Epiphanius of Cyprus (fol.
                     31ra)
 II-4) Anaphora of St Athanasius of Alexandria (fol. 38va)
 II-5)
                     Anaphora of St John, son of Thunder (fol. 54vb)
 II-6) Anaphora of St Jacob
                     of Serug (fol. 68va)
 II-7) Anaphora of St John Chrysostom (fol. 75va)
                     II-8) Anaphora of St Gregory (“Hosanna-liturgy of St Gregory”) (fol.
                     83vb).</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Because of misplacement or absence of many folios, for the constituent
                        texts only the incipit pages are indicated in Short content.</note>
                     <note>Text II-1, explicit of previous text (<locus target="#4rb">4rb-</locus>va): ንጽሕት፡ በድንግልና፡ ሕሊና፡ ወበድንግልና፡ ሥጋሃ፡ ሕትምት፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡
                        አሜን፨</note>
                     <note>Text II-2, explicit of previous text (<locus target="#18vb">18vb</locus>): ዘቦቱ፡ ለከ፡ ምስሌሁ፡ ወምስለ፡ ቅዱስ፡ መንፈስ፡ ስብሐት፡ ወእኂዝ፡ ይእዜኒ፡ ወዘልፈኒ፡
                        ወለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨</note>
                     <note>Text II-3, explicit of previous text (<locus target="#31ra">31ra</locus>): አንተ፡ ዘአቅረብከነ፡ ቅመዝ፡ ምሥጢር፡ ለከ፡ ስብሐት፡ ወክብር፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡
                        አሜን፨</note>
                     <note>Text II-4, explicit of previous text (<locus target="#38vb">38vb</locus>): ኀቤከ፡ እጸርሕ፡ ኀቤከ፡ ነአወይ፡ ኀቤከ፡ ንትመሐለል፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨</note>
                     <note>Text II-5, explicit of previous text (<locus target="#54va">54va-</locus>vb): ኦቅድስት፡ ንኢ፡ ኀቤነ፡ ለለሰሙኑ፡ ከመ፡ ንትፈሣሕ፡ ብኪ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡
                        አሜን፨</note>
                     <note>Text II-6, explicit of previous text (<locus target="#68va">68va</locus>): ለሴስዮ፡ ነፍስት፡ ወሥጋት፡ ወመናፍስቲሆሙ፡ ዘእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዘቦቱ፡ ለከ፡
                        በል፨</note>
                     <note>Text II-7, explicit of previous text (<locus target="#75va">75va</locus>): አብርህ፡ አዕይንተ፡ ዕውራኒሆሙ፡ አስምዕ፡ እዝነ፡ ጽሙማኒሆሙ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡
                        አሜን፨</note>
                     <note>Text II-8, explicit of previous text (<locus target="#83va">83va-</locus>vb): በላዕክሙ፡ ወጸገክሙ፡ ሰተይክሙ፡ ወረወይክሙ፡ በሰላም፡ እትው፡ ውስተ፡ አብያቲክሙ፡
                        እግዚአብሔር፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስሌክሙ፨</note>
                  </msItem>
