                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; name of the Metropolitan; name of the
                           donor in supplication formulas; incipits of the constituent texts;
                           directives for the ministers; most of the abbreviations; elements of the
                           punctuation signs and Ethiopic numbers.
 
 The incipits of some
                           of the constituent texts are written alternately in red and black lines
                           (s. fols. 19ra, 68va, etc.).</seg>
